15 jurisdiction on a transportation network service; and
16 (iii) submit to the Comptroller no later than 30 days after the end of
17 a calendar quarter, or as otherwise specified by the Comptroller in regulations:
18 1. the assessments and other revenues collected by the
19 transportation network company on behalf of the transportation network operators;
20 2. the allocation of the assessments and other revenues
21 attributable to each county or municipal corporation that has imposed an assessment based
