23 3. under oath, a certification that it has submitted the correct
24 amount of assessments and revenues.
25 (3) (i) Subject to subparagraph (ii) of this paragraph, from the
26 assessments and revenues imposed by counties and municipal corporations, the
27 Comptroller shall distribute each quarter the amount necessary to administer the
