29 (ii) The amount distributed to the administrative cost account may
30 not exceed 5% of the revenue from the assessments and other revenue.
31 (4) After making the distribution required by paragraph (3) of this
32 subsection, within 45 days of the end of each calendar quarter, the Comptroller shall
33 distribute the remaining revenue to:

